# .worktreeinclude — copy to `.worktreeinclude` and edit.
#
# Git-ignored files are NOT copied into a new worktree by default, so a fresh
# worktree can't run without its env/secrets. List the git-ignored files each new
# worktree needs; Claude Code seeds them into every worktree it creates.
#
# One glob per line. Examples:

.env.local
.env.development.local
# .npmrc
# certs/localhost.pem
